  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK376">
<l>pariyiṉu mākāvām pālalla vuyttuc </l>
<l>coriyiṉum pōkā tama</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whatever is not conferred by fate cannot be preserved although it be guarded with most painful care; and that, which fate has made his, cannot be lost, although one should even take it and throw it away.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
